sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Entry as aw_wash.py
    participant Builder as PipelineBuilder
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Reader as AWJsonReader
    participant Parser as ASTParseStage + AWParser
    participant Extractor as DocstringExtractStage + AWDocstringParser
    participant Enrich as AWEnrichStage
    participant Writer as AWAggregateWriter

    User->>Entry: --input ./aw_input.json --output ./output
    Entry->>Builder: build_aw_pipeline(config)
    Builder-->>Pipeline: 构建完成的管道
    Entry->>Pipeline: run(config)

    Pipeline->>Reader: process(config)
    Note right of Reader: 读取 JSON 中的文件路径列表, 加载所有源文件
    Reader-->>Pipeline: List[RawSourceFile]

    Pipeline->>Parser: process(raw_files)
    Note right of Parser: AST 定位所有 aw_* 函数, 提取函数名和源码
    Parser-->>Pipeline: List[Tuple]

    Pipeline->>Extractor: process(parsed_data)
    Note right of Extractor: 解析 docstring 提取函数功能描述
    Extractor-->>Pipeline: List[Tuple]

    Pipeline->>Enrich: process(structured_data)
    Note right of Enrich: 组装 AWCorpusItem
    Enrich-->>Pipeline: List[AWCorpusItem]

    Pipeline->>Writer: process(corpus_items)
    Note right of Writer: 聚合输出单个 JSON
    Writer-->>Pipeline: 输出文件路径

    Pipeline-->>Entry: 完成
    Entry-->>User: 输出文件路径
